    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "RAG Indexing Workflow\nMonitors a Google Drive folder for new PDF files. When a file is detected, it downloads and extracts the text, splits it into 500-character overlapping chunks, generates vector embeddings for each chunk using Jina AI, and stores them in Pinecone vector database with metadata. This enables semantic search and retrieval for the query workflow.\nStack: Google Drive → n8n → Jina AI (embeddings) → Pinecone (vector storage)",
        "width": 640
      },
